---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import homeArt from '../assets/home-deterministic-random-walk-art.png';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="home">
			<h1 class="sr-only">Deterministic Random Walk</h1>
			<section class="intro" aria-label="Site introduction">
				<div class="intro-copy">
					<p class="kicker">Deterministic Random Walk</p>
					<p class="lead">
						Markets, institutions, and AI systems all operate under uncertainty. The practical
						work is to navigate that randomness without mistaking it for chaos: identify what
						keeps holding, encode it carefully, and leave room for judgment where judgment is
						actually needed.
					</p>
					<p>
						This is the frame behind the name. Investment is partly art because markets are
						noisy, reflexive, and human. It is partly science because decisions still need
						process, evidence, controls, and memory. Production AI has the same shape:
						probabilistic models help where meaning is ambiguous; deterministic engineering
						makes the result repeatable, auditable, and safe to scale.
					</p>
					<p>
						This site is a research log on modernizing investment workflows with
						production-grade AI: how to combine semantic judgment with reliable systems, and
						how to move through randomness without outsourcing discipline to it.
					</p>
					<nav class="home-links" aria-label="Primary pages">
						<a href="/blog">Read the blog</a>
						<a href="/about">About me</a>
						<a href="/rss.xml">RSS feed</a>
					</nav>
				</div>
				<figure class="intro-art">
					<Image
						src={homeArt}
						width={420}
						alt="A fixed rabbit template surrounded by energetic hand-drawn circles."
					/>
					<figcaption>
						A fixed template inside wild circles: one small picture of the whole idea.
					</figcaption>
				</figure>
			</section>
			<section class="featured-series" aria-labelledby="featured-series-title">
				<p class="section-kicker">Featured series</p>
				<h2 id="featured-series-title">
					Start here: Why agents could not replace our production ESG pipeline.
				</h2>
				<div class="series-lists">
					<div>
						<h3>English</h3>
						<ol>
							<li><a href="/blog/why-this-series-exists-en/">Part 0: Why This Series Exists</a></li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/impossible-task-en/">Part 1: The Portfolio Manager’s Impossible Task</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/seven-layers-en/">Part 2: From “Just Throw It at AI” to 7,400 Lines of Code</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/llm-shines-agents-destroy-en/">Part 3A: Where LLMs Shine</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/agents-destroy-orchestration-en/">Part 3B: The 90% Agents Would Destroy</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/honest-comparison-en/">Part 4: An Honest Comparison — Pipeline vs. Agents, by the Numbers</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/research-data-en/">Part 5A: What the Research Actually Says</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/research-frameworks-en/">Part 5B: The Frameworks Behind the Data</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/leverage-gap-en/">Part 6: The Leverage Gap</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/context-accumulation-en/">Part 7: Context Accumulation</a>
							</li>
						</ol>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3>中文</h3>
						<ol>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/why-this-series-exists-zh/">第0篇：这个系列为什么存在</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/impossible-task-zh/">第1篇：投资组合经理的不可能任务</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/seven-layers-zh/">第2篇：从“直接扔给 AI”到 7400 行代码</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/llm-shines-agents-destroy-zh/">第3A篇：LLM 闪耀的地方</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/agents-destroy-orchestration-zh/">第3B篇：智能体会毁掉的 90%</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/honest-comparison-zh/">第4篇：诚实的对比</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/research-data-zh/">第5A篇：研究到底说了什么</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/research-frameworks-zh/">第5B篇：数据背后的框架</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/leverage-gap-zh/">第6篇：杠杆差距</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="/blog/context-accumulation-zh/">第7篇：上下文积累</a>
							</li>
						</ol>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.home {
		width: min(1040px, calc(100% - 2em));
		padding: 3.5em 1em 4em;
	}
	.intro {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(280px, 0.8fr);
		gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem);
		align-items: center;
	}
	.intro-copy {
		max-width: 680px;
	}
	.kicker {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 0.85em;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}
	.lead {
		margin: 0 0 1.1em;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
		font-size: clamp(1.55rem, 4vw, 2.35rem);
		line-height: 1.16;
	}
	.intro-copy p:not(.kicker):not(.lead) {
		max-width: 620px;
		margin: 0 0 1.05em;
		font-size: 1.02em;
		line-height: 1.68;
	}
	.home-links {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1.4em;
	}
	.home-links a {
		text-underline-offset: 0.18em;
		font-weight: 700;
	}
	.intro-art {
		margin: 0;
	}
	.intro-art img {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 420px;
		margin-left: auto;
		border-radius: 8px;
	}
	.intro-art figcaption {
		max-width: 420px;
		margin: 0.75em 0 0 auto;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 0.82em;
		line-height: 1.45;
	}
	.featured-series {
		margin-top: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
		padding-top: 2rem;
		border-top: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
	}
	.section-kicker {
		margin: 0 0 0.65rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 0.82em;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}
	.featured-series h2 {
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 0 1.4rem;
		font-size: clamp(1.55rem, 3vw, 2.1rem);
		letter-spacing: 0;
	}
	.series-lists {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3rem);
	}
	.series-lists h3 {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: 0;
	}
	.series-lists ol {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.45rem;
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
	}
	.series-lists li {
		padding-left: 0.2rem;
		line-height: 1.45;
	}
	.series-lists a {
		text-underline-offset: 0.18em;
	}
	@media (max-width: 820px) {
		.home {
			padding-top: 2em;
		}
		.intro {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		.intro-art img,
		.intro-art figcaption {
			margin-left: 0;
		}
		.series-lists {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
